name: MedBioWeb
overview: MedBioWeb Corp. engages in the ownership and operation of Medbioworld.com, a medical and bioscience resource and reference Internet portal, and FamilyMedicalNet.com, a consumer healthcare Internet portal. It focuses to provide access to in-depth and up-to-date healthcare, medical, and bioscience information for its Internet users. The company, through its Medbioworld.com, provides access to resources that include medical and bioscience news; extensive journal, association, and database listings; professional conference coverage; continuing medical education activities; full-text medical journal articles; and drug and medical literature databases to the physicians, and allied healthcare and bioscience professionals. MedBioWeb, through its FamilyMedicalNet.com, provides consumer access to health and wellness content from the concept of consumers selecting access points to the information on every possible health and medical subject from the Internet. The company is based in Bethesda, Maryland. MedBioWeb Corp. is a subsidiary of Healthnostics, Inc.
